description: Shane Frost returns to NK with a record of 1:1. He may have lost his match against NK regular DJ, but this time he is cocky, confident, and ready for action. He has been working on his upper body strength and has a solid strategy to out maneuver and out power his opponent. Zach Alexander, a two time champ on NK, is gonna have his work cut out for him. He isn’t worried though, he plans to use his quickness to get Shane into several holds and then rank up the points. These men are both really lean, very hung and eager to tear up some ass on the mat. It’s going to be an all out fight for sexual control.
title: Zach Alexander vs Shane Frost
